        },
        {
          "id": 2,
          "type": "text",
          "variant": "paragraph",
          "style": {
            "padding_top": 3,
            "padding_bottom": 3
          },
          "body_html": "<p style=\"line-height: 1.15\">The ORW base specification is designed to provide a universal frame for large scale deployments while maximizing compatibility and sustainability.</p><p style=\"line-height: 1.15\">Click on the markers to explore the core anatomy and features of the Open Rack Wide frame.</p>"
        },
        {
          "id": 3,
          "type": "labeled_graphic",
          "variant": "labeledgraphic",
          "style": {
            "zoom_on_click": true,
            "padding_top": 3,
            "padding_bottom": 3,
            "media_width": "0"
          },
          "items": [
            {
              "title": "44 OpenU Capacity",
              "x": "45.326089167940445",
              "y": "36.910224459981386",
              "icon": "01",
              "description_html": "<p>The ORW frame provides a massive vertical payload area, accommodating up to 44 OpenU of IT gear.</p>"
            },
            {
              "title": "19-inch and 21-inch Compatibility",
              "x": "55.627264492753625",
              "y": "66.1352676661886",
              "icon": "01",
              "description_html": "<p>The rack design features specific cutouts and support brackets, ensuring the frame can support both traditional RU spacing and OpenU vertical spacing.</p>"
            },
            {
              "title": "Sustainability and Hot Aisle Containment",
              "x": "59.714673913043484",
              "y": "14.911434155155495",
              "icon": "01",
              "description_html": "<p>Built with the OCP <strong>sustainability tenet</strong> in mind, the frame incorporates recyclable parts and material efficiencies.</p>"
            }
          ],
          "media": {
